'''Wonderful Biodrinks GmbH''', doing business as '''Wonderful Drinks''', is a beverage manufacturer from [[Austria]] which produces natural [[organic beverages]] that do not contain any added sugar or additives.

They source their ingredients from [[organic farmers]] from [[South Tyrol]], [[Italy]] and [[Spain]]. To obtain additional vitamins and minimise waste the fruits are juiced whole in the peel and the remains from the juicing are dried and recycled. Organic herbs and flowers and Austrian mountain spring water are then added to the juices. Beverages are produced both carbonated and still.

One of their greatest competitors are [https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lemonaid_Beverages Lemonaid Beverages], but particularly Wonderful Drinks' [https://www.wonderfuldrinks.com/en/brands/ich-bin-wasser Ich bin Was?er] contains a lot less sugar and is free from sweeteners and caffeine.<ref>{{Cite web
